    <item>
      <title>华纳兄弟的分拆使 410 亿美元债券面临垃圾债券风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/a-warner-bros-spinoff-could-send-41-billion-of-bonds-to-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博行业研究显示，如果华纳兄弟探索公司决定剥离其同名电影制片厂和流媒体业务，那么该公司 410 亿美元的债券可能会失去投资级评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/a-warner-bros-spinoff-could-send-41-billion-of-bonds-to-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Kakao 创始人涉嫌操纵股票案获准逮捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/arrest-warrant-issued-for-kakao-founder-by-south-korean-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国当局以市场操纵指控向 Kakao Corp. 创始人 Brian Kim 发出了逮捕令，这为他成为多年来韩国最知名的入狱商界人士奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/arrest-warrant-issued-for-kakao-founder-by-south-korean-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 中断为卖空者带来 4.61 亿美元意外收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/crowdstrike-crwd-outage-nets-short-sellers-461-million-windfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周五，大量做空 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的空头获得了回报，因为该公司的一次失败的软件更新引发了全球 IT 中断，导致股价暴跌至 2022 年 11 月以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/crowdstrike-crwd-outage-nets-short-sellers-461-million-windfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:08:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股大跌之际，对冲基金积极削减股票风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hedge-funds-aggressively-cut-risks-in-stocks-amid-big-tech-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球最大的科技公司遭受重创，对冲基金上周以 2021 年 1 月模因股热潮以来最快的速度抛售获利股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hedge-funds-aggressively-cut-risks-in-stocks-amid-big-tech-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PhonePe、Google Pay 将在线支付份额让给新进入者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/phonepe-google-pay-cede-online-payment-share-to-new-entrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着小型企业的崛起，沃尔玛公司旗下的 PhonePe 和 Alphabet 公司旗下的 Google Pay 在 6 月份通过印度统一支付界面处理的总交易量中的份额略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/phonepe-google-pay-cede-online-payment-share-to-new-entrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗技联合创始人赢得法庭胜利，提名其董事长候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/logitech-co-founder-gets-court-win-to-name-his-nominee-for-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗技联合创始人丹尼尔·博雷尔 (Daniel Borel) 赢得一场法庭斗争，将其董事长候选人列入这家瑞士公司即将召开的股东大会的议程，这是这家电脑硬件制造商领导权之争的最新进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/logitech-co-founder-gets-court-win-to-name-his-nominee-for-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Verizon 收入因设备升级减少而低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/verizon-wireless-revenue-gains-boosted-by-broadband-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于升级无线设备的人数减少，威瑞森通信公司 (Verizon Communications Inc.) 公布第二季度营业收入低于分析师预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/verizon-wireless-revenue-gains-boosted-by-broadband-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
